{"tid":680970,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"宛之旅行遊記","createTime":"2018-05-27T15:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T02:34:08.000Z","uid":32,"like":6,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"86ebe2cae6bbf6bd3a996c9cbeb5e25d01f8a90e","tid":680970,"uid":32,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:16:35.000Z","msg":"一月中買咗機票、打算五月尾旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n望穿秋水之後，終於成行啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/231328_79b2a734da7281d4ac9e2f3a95ccb054.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F231328_79b2a734da7281d4ac9e2f3a95ccb054.png&h=65793c39&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n機票望咗好耐，見到$1900多啲就買咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連埋酒店，成個Trip用咗$4000左就搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/231550_d428b2410c473d5c0ee37ff1be1e294e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F231550_d428b2410c473d5c0ee37ff1be1e294e.png&h=6968dd0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/27/231600_6bb86502b8ce760cc69a412dc38d1afa.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F27%2F231600_6bb86502b8ce760cc69a412dc38d1afa.png&h=4a1ec3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見早咗去機場，入咗Lounge食啲嘢先行<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffd6148db0a0e63befdd069d6a93ec265adf9ab2","tid":68097